- Do you hear them?

989
01:27:00,966 --> 01:27:02,426
Go bust them!

990
01:27:05,345 --> 01:27:08,306
Hey, GI, fuck you!

991
01:27:17,733 --> 01:27:19,985
You hear him out there on the wire, man?

992
