993
01:27:24,197 --> 01:27:25,282
You need a flare?

994
01:27:27,284 --> 01:27:28,535
No.

995
01:27:29,911 --> 01:27:31,747
He's close, man.

996
01:27:32,456 --> 01:27:34,332
