1132
01:41:25,121 --> 01:41:28,416
We'll go together on the boat.
We'll go with you.

1133
01:41:28,499 --> 01:41:32,169
We'll go up there, but on the boat. Okay?

1134
01:42:39,236 --> 01:42:41,113
<i>Part of me was
afraid of what I would find</i>

1135
01:42:41,197 --> 01:42:43,199
