1140
01:44:13,664 --> 01:44:14,957
Just keep moving.

1141
01:44:15,666 --> 01:44:19,336
Lance, keep your hands away from the guns.

1142
01:45:46,257 --> 01:45:49,426
It's all right! It's all right!
It's all been approved!

1143
01:45:50,594 --> 01:45:53,848
